              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "1USAPTN"
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB",
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The Maximum Proton Energy was 19 MeV. The Beam Current",
                "Was Measured with the Target Stack Withdrawn from",
                "The Beam."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA",
                "EDEG"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The Proton Energy in Each Foil was Calculated According",
                "To H.A.Bethe Et Al.  Experimental Nuclear Physics,",
                "Vol.1,(WILEY AND SONS,NEW YORK,1953), H.Bichsel Et Al.,",
                "Phys.Rev.105,1788(1957) And V.C.Burkig Et Al.,Phys.Rev.",
                "106,848(1957)."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "At First All Directly Produced Co-Activities were",
                "Separated from Ni. After Ni-57 in the Ni-Fraction",
                "Had Decayed Completely a Second Ni/Co-Separation",
                "Was Performed and Co-57 from the Co-Fraction was",
                "Counted. The Activity Measured was Free of Co-56,",
                "Co-58 and Co-60 As Experimentally Shown."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Data Uncertainty -",
                "The Data-Error Given is the Standard Deviation Due to",
                "Counting Only.",
                "The Cross Sections are Accurate to About 10%, Mainly",
                "Due to Variations in the Beam Current. The Consistency",
                "Of Cross Sections from Different Bombardments is",
                "About 10%.",
                "   Energy Uncertainty -",
                "The Energy Errors Due to Initial Energy Spread (0.25",
                "MEV) And to Straggling are +-0.34 MeV at 8 MeV and",
                "+-0.28 MeV at 14 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "HISTORY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "date": 19770119,
                "history": "C"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "Lakw"
